  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Parents or caregivers of children from 2 to 10 years old attending primary care clinic

          -  Parents or caregivers must be worried about child behaviour or their parenting skills
             and be willing to get professional help

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Children: Pervasive Developmental Disorder, severe intellectual disability or severe
             psychopathology

          -  Caregivers: illiteracy, decompensated severe psychopathology or current psychotherapy
      </textblock>
